<chapter id="chap-Documentation-Ardour_Notes-Goals">
  <title>Goals</title>
  <para>
    Goals for Ardour development and related activities.
  </para>

  <section id="sect-Documentation-Ardour_Notes-Goals-Weekly">
    <title>Weekly Tasks</title>
    <para>
      These are some of the tasks I have in mind for the weekly goals. Each
      week will have corresponding log of the work accomplished.
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Review all commits
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Respond to or Confirm all new bug reports
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Resolve one valid bug from mantis
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Close/Resolve 2 bugs no longer valid
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Write one new Test Case
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Write one new unit test
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Run unit tests
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </section>

  <section id="sect-Documentation-Ardour_Notes-Goals-Monthly">
    <title>Monthly Goals</title>
    <para>
      Monthly Goals related to Ardour
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Complete one song
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Write summary and send to ardour-dev list eventually.
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Perform all Test Cases
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </section>

  <section id="sect-Documentation-Ardour_Notes-Goals-LongTerm">
    <title>Long Term</title>
    <para>
      Long Term Goals for Ardour development
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Employment or other Financial benefits
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          Increase the stability and usability of Ardour
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>
          An official Windows release
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </section>
